Package model.player

Class MoveHistory

java.lang.Object
model.player.MoveHistory
public class MoveHistory
extends java.lang.Object
This class keeps the history of position and level of the worker. Methods are available to establish the last move executed by the player. A note about this class: "Forced" is not "moved". Some God Effects may cause Workers to be "forced" into another space. A Worker that is forced, is not considered to have moved.
